{
  "stem": "15938.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was, but it was children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, even if the child shouted at you 'Dirty Jew,' and 'Smelly Jew' or whatever, you know, it was a part of life.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It-- it wasn't-- if you are a child, you don't take it seriously.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Only when it started to be abusing-- physical and-- and started throwing stones at you and-- and, you know, in winter the snow used to be very, very deep in banks.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So you would have to clear it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Sometimes we used to come out of the house, and the neighbor's snow was piled up on front of our house.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, things like that, and you couldn't get out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, these were little children things, but they were physically hardships.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was very, very hard to live with that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But then, it started to be physical hardship.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There wasn't enough food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were thrown out of the school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If a child bust you up on the street, you didn't matter.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody came to your rescue except your father or brother or whatever.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The boys never went to shul on their own any more, always accompanied by my father.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And sometimes, they cut the electricity and, you know, little things more and more and more and more.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then in 1942, we started getting the people who were coming over the border and telling us these horror stories about Poland.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I remember two girls walked in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they started telling us stories of what's happening in Poland.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And these are young girls, and they sat on our bed and telling us these stories.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They dig trenches, and they shoot you in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they come and take people away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they kill them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And-- horror stories.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
